ications (CVs) - at this stage, we will select the CVs which will cover most of the features we indicated in the offer, and then contact selected candidates</li><li>Step 2 Preparing a recruitment task</li><li>Step 3 Recruitment interview<br><br></li></ul><strong>We offer a contract of mandate or a B2B contract.<br><br></strong><strong>Please send your CV in English.</strong><br/><br/>Please mention the word **ENTERTAINING** and tag RMjAuMTc0LjY3LjY1 when applying to show you read the job post completely (#RMjAuMTc0LjY3LjY1). This is a beta feature to avoid spam applicants. Companies can search these words to find applicants that read this and see they're human.", 'location': 'Warszawa, Warszawa, Woj. Mazowieckie, Polska', 'apply_url': 'https://remoteOK.com/remote-jobs/remote-copywriting-lead-freelance-estorelabs-1133354', 'salary_min': 0, 'salary_max': 0, 'logo': '', 'url': 'https://remoteOK.com/remote-jobs/remote-copywriting-lead-freelance-estorelabs-1133354'}, {'slug': 'remote-skilled-handyman-red-deer-polytechnic-1133389', 'id': '1133389', 'epoch': 1781262803, 'date': '2026-06-12T11:13:23+00:00', 'company': 'Red Deer Polytechnic', 'company_logo': '', 'position': 'Skilled Handyman', 'tags': ['medical', 'full time', 'education', 'non tech', 'customer support', 'dev', 'marketing', 'digital nomad'], 'description': "<strong>Benefits:<br><br></strong><ul><li>Company parties</li><li>Competitive salary</li><li>Flexible schedule</li><li>Free food &amp; snacks</li><li>Free uniforms<br><br><br></li></ul>If you love working with your hands, enjoy fixing things, and take pride in a job well done, this is the perfect opportunity for you!<br><br>At <strong>Handyman Connection</strong>, we connect skilled handymen and handywomen with steady, high-quality workâ\x80\x94without the headaches of running a business. You wonâ\x80\x99t have to worry about finding jobs, chasing payments, or dealing with customers on your own. We take care of that so you can focus on doing what you love.