 English level (C1). French is a very strong plus.</li></ul>\nð\x9f\x8c± What we offer<p>â\x9c¨ A key role in a fast-growing international SaaS company ð\x9f\x8c\x8d A diverse, global team and collaborative culture ð\x9f\x92¡ Real ownership and autonomy to drive impact ð\x9f\x92\x8e Beyond the Salary:</p><ul><li>Comprehensive Medical Insurance.</li><li>OpenUp platform for your mental well-being.</li><li>Cobee for flexible compensation (meals, transport, etc.).</li><li>Language classes to keep you growing.</li><li>A flexible work model</li></ul><br/><br/>Please mention the word **HONORING** and tag RMjAuMTc0LjY3LjY1 when applying to show you read the job post completely (#RMjAuMTc0LjY3LjY1). This is a beta feature to avoid spam applicants. Companies can search these words to find applicants that read this and see they're human.", 'location': '', 'apply_url': 'https://remoteOK.com/remote-jobs/remote-customer-success-manager-senior-orquest-retail-smart-planning-1133280', 'salary_min': 0, 'salary_max': 0, 'logo': '', 'url': 'https://remoteOK.com/remote-jobs/remote-customer-success-manager-senior-orquest-retail-smart-planning-1133280'}, {'slug': 'remote-civil-engineer-en-8-42-credence-1133279', 'id': '1133279', 'epoch': 1781193624, 'date': '2026-06-11T16:00:24+00:00', 'company': 'Credence', 'company_logo': '', 'position': 'Civil Engineer EN 8.42', 'tags': ['design', 'education', 'technical', 'customer support', 'virtual assistant', 'exec', 'medical', 'engineer', 'part time', 'digital nomad'], 'description': "<p></p><p>Overview</p><p>At Credence, we support our clientsâ\x80\x99 mission-critical needs, powered by technology. We provide cutting-edge solutions, including AI/ML, enterprise modernization, and advanced intelligence capabilities, to the largest defense and health federal organizations. Through partnership and trust, we increase mission success for war-fighters and secure our nation for a better future.</p><p>Â\xa0We are privately held, are repeatedly recognized 